
To compile sme2smj-lexeme.hfst, do:

hfst-xfst -F sme2smj-lexeme.xfscript

To analyse, do:

echo aktiiva|hfst-lookup -q sme2smj-lexeme.hfst


To compile 3 different files (for A, N, V ), do the following:

For the the lines 327 - 369, comment in and out the lines marked
A_ONLY and V_OMLY in order to get converters from A and V.

The compilation script gives the output file
sme2smj-lexeme.hfst

Before changig the code, rename the generated hfst file to e.g.
sme2smj-A-lexeme.hfst
sme2smj-V-lexeme.hfst

(if you don't, the former output will be overwritten)



